{"tid":616413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港法律已經可以保障到台灣人民了，恐嚇炸台中車站16歲仔天水圍被捕","createTime":"2018-04-04T07:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T08:16:31.000Z","uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"672d73f09985cc8910c80d802771b9017a7c156e","tid":616413,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"涉慫恿2學生Fb留言炸台中火車站及刺殺台中市長，<span style=\"color: red;\">16歲仔天水圍落網</span>。警方於上周五(3月30日)在天水圍一處拘捕姓袁(16歲)少年，涉嫌「有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦」。該名少年已獲准保釋候查，4月下旬須向警方報到，案件由網絡安全及科技罪案調查科跟進。<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，袁涉嫌早前慫恿台灣2名中學生，在Facebook一個手機遊戲群組內，貼出「炸掉台中火車站，刺殺市長林佳龍</span>」等留言，造成社會恐慌。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180404/bkn-20180404000747117-0404_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180404%2Fbkn-20180404000747117-0404_00822_001.html&d=EQeDkbj5XTFf33Q5RgtclZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=194b15b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180404/bkn-20180404000747117-0404_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"50523e3cca5cdefb47f3b359239cc9b3aa0e8ff1","tid":616413,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"殺人就算Q數唔引渡<br />\n講句嘢要殺民進黨市長就要俾人拉<br />\n民進黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06bd28c397c6fec46c272425c19e69e25fe5ee6","tid":616413,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"有理由相信係香港密謀或者策劃犯罪，就算將會係外國發生都係拉得架喎。"},{"pid":"0d8d8a114bfa6913619faaf6613d1c6fb3a57f2c","tid":616413,"uid":29804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"50523e3cca5cdefb47f3b359239cc9b3aa0e8ff1","tid":616413,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"殺人就算Q數唔引渡<br />\n講句嘢要殺民進黨市長就要俾人拉<br />\n民進黨<